================================================================================
 ESTIMATED TIMELINE
================================================================================

  Phase 1 (Backend Integration):     2-3 weeks
  Phase 2 (Maps & Location):         1-2 weeks
  Phase 3 (Expense Tracking):        1-2 weeks
  Phase 4 (AI & Smart Features):     2-3 weeks
  Phase 5 (Community Features):      1-2 weeks
  Phase 6 (Admin & Management):      2-3 weeks
  Phase 7 (Polish & Production):     1-2 weeks

  Total estimated development time:  10-17 weeks

  Note: Phases can overlap. Phase 1 is strictly sequential (must complete
  before others). Phases 2-6 can be partially parallelized.
